I wrote very detailed wikis every week about goals and current situation, and kept reporting to my PO and CEO.

75
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:38,000
After doing that for about two months, I think they also realized that this wasn't working.

76
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:46,000
So we decided to set up the roadmap again, and in a way, I could be delta

77
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:48,000
but I couldn't be echo.

78
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:54,000
I'm not someone with great business sense or a strategist.

79
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:58,000
I might be good at implementation. That's what I felt.

80
00:07:58,000 --> 00:08:06,000
So let's start from scratch again. Literacy came up again at that time

