82
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:12,000
It was really confusing.

83
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:20,000
I was a coder, and I didn't think I knew enough to teach anyone.

84
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:24,000
This was around February this year.

85
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:30,000
There was a lot of interest in developing and tuning models.

86
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:34,000
I don't have a machine learning background, so what can I teach?

87
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:36,000
What can I show people?

88
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:40,000
I was in that kind of vague state.

